After adding checksum support in VLOG, I found GDR will result in increasing loss for GPU when checksum is disabled. It seems that some synchronisation is required for truly direct DMA between NIC and GPU, and the stream executor seems to be place for me to look into.

I am looking into the GDR docs [here](http://docs.nvidia.com/cuda/gpudirect-rdma/index.html#sync-behavior). 

